      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Obed - Eedomam prett\nDeenas-Widdu/ un winna Deh-\nleem pee ta Namina Esupim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Supinam un Oſam prett\nWakkarapuffi pee tahm Wahr-\ntim / kur staiga us Dedsamo-\nUppuru Eelas/ kur Wafts prett\nWafti stahw.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Prett Rihteem bija fetchi\nLewitti/ prett Seemetapuffi / ik-\nDeenas tfchetri / prett Deenas-\nWiddu ikdeenas tschetri/ bet pee\nEsupini pa dtweem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pee Parwara prett Wak-\nkarapuffi bija tfchetri pee Eelas/\nun diwi pee Parwara.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Schihs irr to Wahrtu-\nSargu Kahrtas / no to Kori-\ntexu Behrneem / un no Me-\nrata Behrneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir no teem Lewiteem bi-\nja Afijus pahr tahm Deetwa\nNamma Mantahin/ un pahr to\nfwehtitu Leetu Mantahin.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "No Laëdaxa Behrneem/\nLaëdaxa ta Gersonitera Behr-\nneem: No Laëdaxa btja to Teh-\nwo Nammu Wirfneeki tee Jeki-\nclitert.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "To Jekiçlitertu Behrni\nbtja: Setams un winna Brah-\nlis Joëls / pahr ta KUNGA\nNamina Mantahin.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Starp teem Amramite-\nxeem/ Jezeartexeem/ Gebronite-\nxeem un Uſielitexeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bija Sebuëls/ Gerson\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet winna Brahlins\nlieſexam bija weens Dehls R\nbijus/ ta Dehls bija Jesajus\nDehls bija Jorams/ ta Dehls\nja Sikrus / ta Dehls bija\nlomits.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 26,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Schis Selomits un u\nna Brahti bija pahr wiſſ\nMantahm to fwehtu Leetu\ntas Kehnisch Dahwids bij f\nfijs/ lihds ar teem Wirfneek\nto Tehwo Naminu/ un ar t\nAhwersteem un Kapteinem,\nzitteem Karra Wirfneefeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 27,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No teem Karreem un L\npitchanahm bij tee tohs fwe-\nschi/ ta KUNGA Naminu\ntaisficht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 28,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ir wiſſu / ko Sam-\ntas Redsetajs bij fwehtijs /\nSaule Kiſa Dehls/ un Abr\nNera Dehls/ un Joabs Zeru\nDehls/ wiſſ/ kas fwehtihfs b\ntas btja Selomitam un wi-\nBrahfeem Rohka.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 29,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No teem Jezeartiter\nbija Kenanijus un winna D\npahr to Darbu/ kas ahra p\nIsraëlu bij jadarra par usr\ngeem un Teefatejeem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 30,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "No teem Gebroniter\nbija Asabijus un winna Br\nti/ tikkuſcht Laudis / tuhkſco\nun feptinsints pahr Isr-\nWalstin/ tchaï Jardana M-\nprett Wakkarapufft / pahr w\nDarbu ta KUNGA/untaim\nnaim par Kalpoſchannu.\n"
    }
  ],
